They put sprinklers on! The fire went out!
When the car is started, get those RPMs up and disable the jack.
That's kind of what I said. But he's tough like an old shoe, our Vlad.
It's probably right under your noses, friends.
Not perfect, but seven points for effort!
That should'a been hydrogen chloride!
First, you need to get onto the ranch. Thermite should take care of that gate.
What's taking so long!?
Oh I'm going with caustic soda.
Kak! The car alarm went off! No more sneaking around then.
Charon is waiting for you, guys! Get moving!
14 left.
This is fine, we'll take it.
I'm just guessing at this point... These internet descriptions are iffy.
It's the cops! Gang, deal with them! Protect Charon!
That's ten!
I have been in the bank one time, a few years ago. The bank manager is an idiot. He keeps his access key in a personal safe, but I don't remember where.
You move, and you'll be in Igors bed before you can say oh shit"."
Don't give the cops a damn thing. Just signal Hectors guys with the floodlights in the warehouse and get that coke onto the speedboat. Nothing fancy here.
I have been in the bank one time, a few years ago. The bank manager is an idiot. He keeps his access key in a personal safe, but I don't actually remember where.
The hard drive is right inside that server room!
We got twelve. Twelve bags!
Don't' forget to blow up that floor, yeah?
Seeing a lot of SWAT vans rolling in. Those kaks can bring this chopper down. I can't pick you up here. But I have a plan...
Good. Last one. Get to it friends!
Domkop courier didn't stash the winch! He's gonna get it later. Ok friends, I'll have one coming shortly by train.
The helicopter is coming. Just hold on a little longer!
The real present was the friends we made along the way. And the power-up you just got!
No les dejen escapar!
Are you guys ready to get the hell out?
Great, those sprinklers will put out the fire.
The power, friends. Restart it!
Keep it moving in there.
We had agreed on more than this.
Make the dwankie choke and cough.
Here's the deal...
Get to the platform.
Guys! You got one minute!
If the intel is correct the test subjects that you need to scan are identical.
Put the delivery in the car...
Made a bad bad step, amigo.
Move into the warehouse.
Ok friends, you're going to like this! A little smash and grab in the dead of winter, yeah?
I see one!
Hey, assholes. I'm enjoying a Martini in here! How you like that?
Get the fuck outta here!
Typical, I'm being locked out of the network. Must be a firewall. See if you can bypass it from another terminal.
What the hell!? Hey, you wanna look where you're throwing that stuff!
Double time, y'all! Got word the Army's fixin' to blow up the railroad tracks. A demolition team is on it's way!
Great. Now crack those trucks open. Let's see what Vlad was shipping.
Take cover guys! It's gonna blow!
That's not optimal... but it happened. Go to the balcony!
Be ready!

All right, time to be careful. There's another guard patrolling the area. I'm betting he's looking for his missing buddies. Whatever happens, do not kill this man. You understand? Don't kill him or we're screwed.
That was easy. Okay, deploy your drill and get that safe open.
Twitch here, about to return.
So he's a car freak. Well... soon he will be a dead car freak.
Thirty seconds, gang.
Well, if you had to go loud, best to do it properly, and that was some outstanding action. You got the whole database. Sifting through the info now...
Now get to the ICU. Find and listen to Dr. Schneider, the patient we're looking for should have blood poisoning and an abnormal heart rate.
Found him! He's in Shaw!
Give up Mr. Sturr, we will be gentle.
Your back's against the goddamn wall!
Ok. Got him. Name, social security number, name of his dog... Find him. Check the screen in IT. Oh, and he's a slot machine addict, might be a good place to start looking.
You can't run around opening random doors. Maybe it's listed somewhere?
First of all, besides from that starter kit, another package is awaiting you in the back alley.
I'm there in three minutes!
OK, this is getting too hot. The van is leaving. I'll get you a chopper. Stay cool.
One, two, cops are coming for you...
Bain will make the call with the pass phrase.
Let me patch in the chopper pilot now!
Our bird will be near the train yard any moment. Be ready!
How's the refueling going?
You probably want to hunker down by the warehouse.
Over there. The First World Bank. Okay, get out and get to work.
We should find a way to distract those guards.
Come with me.
Any luck finding that walkie talkie?
C'mon, let's get you out of here. Oh how is he even still alive?
Your buddy needs your help! Go!
We need to test SERA's oil batches to see which one's the purest. Take a sample from the Extraction Room.
They interrupted the computer. You gotta protect it, guys!
Get to the breaker box.
What in the gods' names is.... I can't believe it... is that...? Ach! Bekakin' bastards! Get out of there, friends!
Now detonate the C4 in the main hall. Place it right above the vault. Hard to say exactly where that is. Two possible spots. Pray for a bit of luck.
Now get out of there!
Oh, and there are probably rival Russian mobsters here. I know, Vlad is not being forthcoming with me either.
Dunno what that is, but we got it. Now, back to the car!
Right, now open those warehouse doors and go to Vlad.
We can settle for this, let's go...
Hustle that gold onto the roof, get it into the bag on the zipline, we're taking it.
Your mother knows less than a Murmansk whore. Let them hear. Let them come!
Maybe it will unlock the Evidence Room. Take it and go find it.
We need our train pointing in the right direction! Go hack the controls to that turntable!
Look around for a ladder. I'm sure that with energy properly applied to a search you will profit. For sure.
That's the alarm. Screw the keycards - we're blowing the gate. Bile is close by. Drop a signal flare, and he'll drop the C4.
Guys!
Now you got to find a way inside.
The game is on, motherfuckers!
Glad I got an American car. Those foreign jobs never have enough trunk space.
We gotta turn those lights back. Get on it!
Go, men - and get me what I want. The night out has just begun!
Its vent goes right to the Security Center.
Make sure no cop or SWAT sees the hacking device, don't let them near the ballot machine truck!
Bags! We need more bags!
Hurry up and get to the West Wing, chop chop!
As soon as you get the cash, I'm signalling the pick-up guy to come drive by.
One of those crates holds the statue. See if you can find a crowbar to open it with, but we were told they are probably rigged, so be careful.
Looks like the right one alright. Now get it open and we do the next bit in style.
Three's the charm, on some occasions.
Ride through the gate and you'll be safe!
Find the manhole out in the parking lot. You're going subterranean.
His party is over - I want all his money for his treason. You go in and you take all from him. Find the safe and fast.
They're pretty antsy - just get the paintings on the table and keep both eyes open for anything weird.
Can't go having that saw there friends, get it off, yeah?
Don't forget that Garrett will be back soon.
Open ears. The safes are in the trucks. I need every single one to come out. Safely. Now, close ears. Get safes.
Quickly guys, find him and take him out!
Right, now find a way into the mansion.
Let me remind you. Look for a keycard if you want to get access to the roofs. Kak...
Who the hell do you think you are!?
30 seconds, get to the entrance!
Do it, people!
OK, find the CFO. He's got the master code!
Shush! What's that sound... Hmm, seems, nah seems OK.
That's it, guys. This will take some time. Just make sure the power stays on.
You need to dismantle that turret.
An amount of loot is at a Murkywater facility in the desert. We shall combine forces to take it.
The weapon is ready, so hit the fire button and melt that door.
They are coming in from the forest next to the road! Keep them away!
The manager's probably crapping his black threads somewhere. Find him. Get his keycard.
Damn, it crashed again. Restart the data scrambling!
Get searching the wagons. You can expect a fast response from the cops. Remember, you're looking for the wagon with the vault!
No time to waste, we got to leave!
I'm in, might take a few to get the door open.
We were close, but....time to bail. Still get my cut, right?
I have urgent need. My business has been interrupted and police is on my goods.
Do you see the flash drive? It should be in a laptop or something.
However, it doesn't run well on batteries, so you gotta plug it into a proper socket.
We got it. Pretty nice flying from my guy as well. Let's use him again sometime.
Activate the crane. I sure hope this works!
Jingle bells! The cops all smell! We're gonna steal their gifts! Shake the tree! Give the presents to me! But look out, 'cause the cops will be pissed!
More will be coming soon.
They might have his cabin listed in a computer on the crew deck.
Listen up! The cops are bringing in a lot of people to block the tracks up ahead, so you really need to go. Bring the BCI tech and head back to Bile!
That's it. I have to send a team over and notify the police.
It's a roach motel - only the roaches are Russian mobsters. No matter. Get in there and put them down.
Now we need to know who's in this room, steal their keycard. I'll need a guest list. Download that from a terminal in reception. Grab a USB.
Need the Moretta's frequency, guys. Get searching terminals.
To the pillar guys!
Something's wrong with the drill. Start it again!
Hurry up! Breach the elevator and get to the penthouse!
Good. The computer is working again without interruption.
Put them down!
Now just raise the balloon and let the pilot do the rest.
The thermite has melted a hole straight into the vault, just as planned. Jump down and grab the cash!
Vault's not open yet... Dammit.
Ready whenever you are.
There we go! Just like one of those Russian doll-things. Take the box and keep it safe.
Don't mess around...
These chicks, you know, you know how much that is? Each day? But hey, you know, it's worth it.
That's all we need, friends. Well done, now make your way out.
This is an FBI auxiliary office. The hornet's nest. For the love of God stay quiet. First thing, get inside.
Restart the countdown.
You need to prepare the next part of the formula.
Yeah, it's ten thousand dollars a day.
Just grab that loot and let's get it out of here.
How it got up there is a mystery.
Thanks, it's good to work with professionals.
I can see the plume from here, what is that? Is it snow?!
He did it, gang. You can grab more loot if you want or you get on those bikes and escape!
Back door looks good. Crack it open with a saw, friends.
The prototype's useless if SERA can just build another. Get to the lab and trash it!
Chopper can't hang around forever, gang. Get there, get out!
What the fuck is this!?
Excellent, guys. It actually feels nice knowing we did something good. But don't get any ideas, we're robbing a bank or something next.
I'm sorry. No. I don't think the pigs would appreciate that. Even if they're dead.
If you don't pick up the phone, they'll send a guard this way!
Ey, don't mess around...
Use the C4 to send those radars tumbling, my friends!
You have to keep them away from the asset.
You'd better find some cover and make sure it's nothing bad.
Hold on guys, I'll send some C4...
This is trouble... I see at least nine guys.
Why do I always get the yappy cellmates...?
All right, gang. I've found some terminals that might have a suitable code. I need you to run a little hack on them.
OK, we're almost done!
You've defeated the seventh wave of cops!
Hey, stay cool, brother.
Vlad wants us to destroy a minimum amount of goods.
Okay, time for the next step in our plan - the C4 from Bile. Wait, let me patch him in. Bile
column3: you there? We need the C4. How long?""

String: The cops cut the power. We need to get it back on.
You guys always know how to throw a good party! Vlad is happy he came along to see this!
Perfect, I can do this. Beginning hacking.
Fuck me!
The system is on lockdown, so that keypad is useless even with a code. You have to brute force your way through that gate.
SWAT on their way. Guess they wanted to talk to Commissar about the battle at the motel.
They cut the power to the house! Lights are down.
Welcome back, Director Stevens.
I think Rust mentioned this room. Maybe there's something useful in there.
It should be caustic soda!
No! I can't take any more, not now!
You gotta take out those bikers!
Even if we blow up the radar, they can still control this from the laptop. We need to hack it.
Pick it up. It's your money that I laundered. Some extra in there for your generous contribution to OVERKILL.
It's an older code, but it checks out...
They just finished flushing ALL the coke. God damn it, gang! We missed out big time!
I have an extraction plan. Go to the parking lot.
Hello? Yes sir, no problems at all. We're just running some tests.
OK, to make things a little more interesting I'm sending this feed live to all the big media outlets while we upload. Lots of coverage.
Like a glove.
Go find who bought the Tin Boy! There should be a bag from the toy store.
Lowering security door.
Keep going!
That should get the process going.
It's muriatic acid.
Excellent. They are blind! Blind as a bat. Though bats are supposed to be blind, and locate prey by echolocation, so that is...
Oil transfer in progress. Hold down the fort!
Come to think of it, I'm kinda thirsty too. Be right back!
Spent the weekend polishing the Longfellow. Took the chief's wife out for a spin. Let her polish the.. you know it, man!
That's 13 bags!
There's no getting through that thing quietly with tools, so you'll have to find a code for it.
The Ln Tiyng freight company warehouse is Vlad's location. No time to waste.
The present died so we can live! Team bonus for everyone!
DUDE you hit like a GIRL!
You're keeping it quiet. Great. Remember - you need keycards.
Gonna give you a faceful of lead!
What are you doing over there?
OK. The access codes seem to have worked.
That's 6, only 2 more.
Hurry down guys. We don't want the police to wreck our ticket for escape.

OK, You're gonna need a thermal drill for this gig. My guy stashed it around the back of the bank. Get it and get to work on the vault. Keep in mind there's security cameras and lots of civilians. Go win the gold, folks.
OK, that's all we need.
No need to sneak around any longer. New plan incoming.
... coming back soon!
Get the Moretta out of the dock. When it's berth, get aboard, get the explosives, get out. Got it?
Keep calm and keep stopping kerels, your ride out is on the way.
Man, I loved coming here as a kid. Made me feel like an adventurer, y'know.
Oh. The best room in the safe house. The vault.
It doesn't look good, guys - it doesn't look good!
They still haven't heard a thing.
Now make sure the elevator doesn't move. Find the fuse box and rewire it.
Set up the buzzsaws. Two on the sides of the panic room and two on the floor below.
Come on, let's get going. Get in.
I see one of 'em!
Ok, you made it so far and the kerels have made an offer. I think we can hold out for more.
Don't be afraid to pick it up...
You made us come for nothin'!?
SWAT! I knew it was too easy!
Blow open the gate between the workshop and the ranch house.
Man, I could really use a beer.
Get inside - we need those cooks.
Get a move on, chops. The laboratory is in a wing opposite the research offices.
That alarm needs to go quiet. Find the switch for it around there, yeah?
Acid, guys, acid. Get some and pour it in there.
The other party is now a minute away.
We got GenSec trucks moving through the suburbs. Go hit 'em.
That's a tunnel entrance if ever I've seen one.
Now get inside that vault, yeah?
What the fuck do you think you are doing?
Guys, get this shit going.
Good work, you chops! Blerrie well done! That's the end of Wang; now pick up that keycard he just dropped.
The code begins with a one, according to my source.
Requesting all guards outside! Someone's wearing socks and sandals! It's hideous!
There... right. He's being kept in a container.
There he is!
I gotta go in a minute!
C'mon, cheer up. It's not over yet, is it?
You piece of shit San Dimas puta! Where the fuck is Miguel? I told you to get him half an hour ago!
Look for a circuit breaker to get the power back up.
And now Mendoza and his goons are down a lot of firepower. Hector's people will face a lot less resistance thanks to you. He might even appreciate us. Well done.
Look around the West Wing for something strong to use on the barrier!
The C4 is in play, gang. Grab it.
Alright. That looks good. Thanks.
Now it's just a matter of time.
Can't leave while the garage doors are closed.
Wang is running away! Looks like he is going to the roof. Move! His time is up.
There's the chopper, gang. Get to it!
All right, you got one of the boxes.
Hey, guys, I'm coming in for a short period of time, so bring me any loot you want to secure.
Loot for the taking...
Kang, a new burner phone and cards have been arranged for you. They are in your cabin.
A rat in their midst has sold them out to the Cobras street gang - vicious pricks that even Hector's people don't deal with. Which is where you come in... Trade the meth with them for the info.
If you find the server room, we can probably bypass the lock.
Now start it up and drive right into that door!
Ok, I'm in! Stand by. This shouldn't take me long.

Now don't forget to tell the guys to be brutal. Make Buluc suffer real good.
Maybe have Jiro samurai-chop his balls or something.
My associate will be in position.
Friends, I'm still trying to sort this. Hang in there.
...and also on the 45 going south, there's been a major accident that's clogging the entire freeway. It's like a war zone out there this morning so you better take a scenic route.
That bag should put us in the black.
Connection lost. What's going on?
Holy fuck!
That's right. C4 each of those dishes.
Lower the goat, or we shoot.
You're getting whacked!
There goes the chopper, but don't worry - it'll be back. In the meantime, let's see if you can track down some more of those presents.
Expertly done, gang. You guys are like shadows.
You wouldn't think that the cartels would bother with such a thing, yeah? Might as well take it with you.
That keycard opens the dock gate. Use it in the control room.

Ach! Their cybersecurity is tight. There's a separate firewall installed, most likely controlled from a critical computer. Xun Kang had a laptop in the meeting room, see if that's the one we're looking for.
You're gonna flood the place?! Gemma said y'all were crazy. I love it!
That's a Lo Pan container.
Good, thank you.
No snoozing, friends. Garrett could be heading back at any time.
See that drive thru window at the side of the bank? There's a manhole there to the sewers. Get down there.
Unrestricted access. Fuckin' get in! Now, get back here. Let's keep this going.
Now you're just showing off.
In the back!
... Put these gringos in the ground!
Great, now start the money maker.
Blerrie, that's the vault from the blueprints.
My bad. It's muriatic acid.
We're done here!
I can't believe this shit!
You should hit them in the head.
Just one more.
I got one!
Yeah, he was a smartass... bragging about his shit again...
Roger. One moment please. Today's code is 8394. Please remember it next time. This is very sensitive information.
Ag man, the pump stopped. Maybe it needs more juice?
Oh, lest I forget, a new phone and business cards are waiting in your cabin.
I reckon you will find keys around there somewhere, yeah?
Great, now down the ramp and get outside.
Keep cool.
We really need what's in that office. You gotta get past that lockdown.
Yes, good...picking up telemetry from the money now. Right on target. Oh, why don't you grab those parachutes there.
Hector wants us to secure at least four bags!
We are prepared to renegotiate the hostage release and have been authorized to make a higher offer!
Head down to the gold stashes and bring all you can carry.
The tunnel entrance should be outside somewhere.
Don't miss that chopper now!
Drill the door, you chops!
Maneuver the crane over the locomotive. It's our best chance for getting out of here!
That was some action movie shit, right there. They told me you were nuts, and you did not disappoint.
See, never doubt my plans.
Today could've been better, guys. But we'll have to deal with Locke eventually. He'll be running from more people than us.
Let the drill do it's job. You do yours.
Deliver the bags!
Feel that bass.

All safely down? Great. Locate the crash site, and see if the pilot's still alive. If he is, you need to get him to a safe place. I'll get a chopper out to pick him up ASAP. A plane doesn't crash out here without causing attention, so you can expect company. Work fast.
Ah, that is the vault guys. That door, we can't get through it this time. But the gold... The gold on the other side! Well, we got to leave it.
Shit! Wrong key!
Man, if we get out of this one, I never want to see the inside of another office building.
The escape driver is coming in by boat to pick you up. Make sure you are over by the small water access near the river.
Hello gentlemen. Our client is very pleased that you agreed to do this with us. But know this - the only way this is going through is if we do it our way.
No doubt Kang could open that safe in a jiffy.
These civilians don't give a crap about you as long as you act normal.
There are millions of crates in there. Yes, millions. You just gotta find the right one. Use a terminal in the IT lab.
Hey, we don't have all day!
More money in our pockets and it should also win us some favor with Locke.
Four
Take care to enter the correct code.
He's going for the laundry room. Follow him!
Gentlemen...
Hey, I'm having trouble with my account on the computer. Do I internet?
Now grab as much of Vlad's merchandise as you can carry and get it out to the garbage truck!
One of Buluc's bodyguards is called Mucho Mike. You believe that shit?
There's the coke. Outstanding, guys! Bag as much as you can.
Where's the stuff, man!
King - you know King - man, that fat bastard sure loved to snort blow.
I'd do some casing before you go in.
Right, here's our way out. Get back upstairs, and C4 the wall into the adjoining building.
We're pissing a lot of cash. Someone's gonna notice.
I'll be here tomorrow as well. Come by and we'll talk.
You need to check the mainframe again for the next artifact.
Almost open. Remember, you deal with the radars, and I will prepare the helicopter.
The cartel requests your assistance again. Now we are going on offense, as you say in football. Las Mendozas and the FBI will regret not eliminating me when I was weak. For I am strong now.
I've stowed some plastic explosive in the DeLorean. You can use it to make that gas station go up like the Tsar Bomba!
The door to Garrett's office is locked, but see if you can bypass it through nearby security boxes.
If you cut power to the nearby electric box, those detectors should go down.
That explosion will have it raining crystals for weeks.
Any luck yet?
Take the sniper out, guys!
Great, now get into that Falcogini. I'll clear the road. Heads down!
Get Vlad out of those restraints!
Now set up the camera and record it. Hector likes quality I guess.
The door is open! Now, time to put this caper to bed. Deal with him.
Four!
Good afternoon. Roberts bank. How can I help you?
Could be that the code is related to Garrett's crusade against us, yeah?
We got a fucking police caravan on our ass!
Five thousand dollars, guys.
I'm going to make you bleed!
I see one!
The oil transfer can't continue while the firewall's active.
What's taking so long!?
Shit, I forgot something. If you find any tapes in that vault, take them too please... uh I.. I don't know, maybe... maybe burn them somewhere later, OK?
Think you're going to do this if you keep it up.
Ten more seconds - then I'm gone!
Plan B guys! Just get that server.
The pass phrase is needed when you call Ernesto Sosa. It should be there.
Ka-pow motherfuckers!
There's one!
Get to the chopper!
Look at that. A lot of rich people up there, enjoying themselves.
Ooh, nice bit of hardware, that! Going to be useful for sure!
I've already got interested parties lined up to take the bullion. I'll also dig up what I can regarding this blueprint.
Keep me informed of our progress.
Find the wagons marked with the shipping company from the manifest.
Now find the car keys. Wang probably has them locked away.
Send the gas through the building ventilation.
Check the backrooms.
Hey, hurry up will you!
You've only got a small bit of time before the kerels find you.
OK, your getaway is standing by. Bail now, or use it to clear out the ammo. Your call.
Sure there's gotta be a good reason that goat is up in the fan. Just find the circuit box. Stop the fan.
Awesome job gang! Last step - you need to dismantle the server and bring it to the car.
Hmm... not sure where this entrance is exactly, but if you poke around a bit, maybe you can find it.
You fuck with me? I fuck you! You!
Won't make that mistake again. Go and reactivate my transfer.
That's it for that rat fucking shite Hector. How could he turn like that? Cowardly twat. Well done lads.
Valentine's computer should be nearby.
It is a moderate ambition, I admit, but one that I find pleasing.
We need hydrogen chloride!
Two more!
You see that bridge? I'm dropping the cage over there.
The deal's off!
Not sure they're the same as the others.
The van is right around the corner. It'll be there in one minute.
The containers are ready for you. Get searching.
Throw the bag on the table.
Go on, search the harbor office computer system.
Keep looking for the armory!

When building a custom bike, it's all about the details, baby. And what's more bad-ass than a chrome fucking skull? Am I right or am I right? I saw a special made one inside the clubhouse. Get it for me.
Ah, the door opens! Now, let us proceed into the inner complex with speed and violence.
Hook me up. I should be able to get into their system from here.
Hold 'em back!
Ok guys, go across the roof!
I will hold you to that, you chop!
Have you found the code yet? Look around real good.
Now swipe the card on the panel in the other control room. Get that gate open.
... I'll come back in no-time!
I remember when you could smoke in the operating room. Once I put on that damn dress I tell ya...
Get that C4 planted in the Gambling Hall, gang.
Goddamn roadworks! Find a way to bridge it.
Take a look around and see if you can find a clue on how to crack that code. Check the workstations.
The train's ready for the cargo. Check the wagons. Probably loaded. Might find something worthwhile.
... you don't think our time's important?
OK, doctors - bring your MIT skills. Figure out which one is the correct fusion engine. Go!
Just gotta keep looking until you find the laptop.
Damn! Alright, I'm sending the drill.
Prepare to get fucked up!
Get in there quick and find a way into the cellar.
Nothing, eh? Nada, you get nothing...
You got nine cameras to take care of.
Where is it?
Put these suckers in the ground!
Nine!
They'll keep the keycard in a safe, no doubt.
Package on the ground. Good luck out there!
Come on, guys!
Almost there, I'm ready in 30 seconds!
Chopper's back in the area. Watch for it.
I'm one minute away!
The CSO's got to be on site for the big event. Maybe there's a schedule in his office.
Data's scrambled. Well done. Even if they figure it was deliberate, the results are unusable. Great job.
Hello, B-uhm... nurse Bain speaking. What do you need?
Let's find that vault, chop chop.
The GenSec truck's a bonus. A keycard in it would be a sweeter bonus.
Enter MercyKill.
You heard her. I've done a little homework and marked some terminals that should have the 4-digit code in 'em somewhere.
Ok, that's the one, there he is! Let him out, yeah?
More snipers are moving in.
Moretta. This is Port Washington radio. One zero one E. Over.
Use the kitchen blender to make an evidence cocktail.
19 bags left!
Look for the power room to rewire the fuse box.
This is a dock... so I reckon there must be equipment around there to move containers with!
I'll send you home to your momma in little pieces!
A prudent person foresees the danger ahead and takes precautions; the simpleton goes blindly on and suffers the consequences. I'm quoting the Holy Book.
I got it.
They say he's taking money from the clowns.
The more guns you can grab, the better!
Go ahead and burn it. I know, it's sad...
Ah, you fucked it up. No presents for you.

Blast blew wagons everywhere. Might be loot in some of 'em. And check 'em for any C4. You'll need it soon.
Oh, almost forgot. You'll need to use a blowtorch to get inside.

Wonderful, my friends. Thank you. Thank you for helping Vlad with these things. Coyopas will be furious, but I don't give a shit. It's no matter. The time for dealing with them will come later. Well, I will be in touch soon. There is more for you to do down there.
Just took a .50 cal. Fuck! I'm going down.
Just follow me and stay out of sight. God, I wish I had a drink.
Damn it, one of us got caught and placed in custody! Bain, we need a new escape vehicle!
Don't kill him now. All will be in vain!
I dunno... There's some weird... It's probably nothing.
Bring more, this is not all of it.
That's four.
Looks like that Kang-dwankie has locked himself in the meeting room. Smash your way inside.
Load the Neo-2 in our getaway van. Finders keepers, eh?
A storage closet would be a good place to put the listening device.
That's the last box. Cutting the power. Done! Lasers are down! Move on!
Our driver has pulled the ambulance over and ran for it. And here comes the target, right on schedule...
I'll tell you what. We were never gonna deal with you guys! We'll take it all!
Guys, we got cops so far up our ass they are practically sitting on my fucking lap!!
We need that oil sample! Go to the Extraction Room!
Motherfuckers! Stop that!
Are you so dumb that the third pallet - a fucking inanimated object - can hide from you? Find that cunt.
That's 13 bags!
Where is Li Deng?
... then, we'll trade.
I don't care what you have to do. Shoot the fuckers.
OK, we need the minimum cash amount. Once we have that, I'll send a car for you. Now if you want to stick around and get more, be my guest.
Get out of there, kakspul of trouble is coming!
What are you waiting for? Set up the bomb.
Ok you chops, get into that bird!
... but get more if you can!
The bypass needs to be restarted.
Open sesame, friends!
The truck is in the slaughterhouse. There's C4 stashed in those bins. Grab it and bust in.
We need more C4 on the fourth floor and the roof.
And that is the end. Comrade Asshole is dead. Chopper is in-bound. Great work today. The Dentist, and Hoxton, will thank you.
Just....goat noises"! Screaming. Well
column3: wouldn't you with 5lbs of coke up your ass?"

String: Swell, these will make Cabot happy after all this is done.
It should be hydrogen chloride instead.
Can't unlock the doors until you patch in properly.
There's one!
Nice, jewels and tiara. Time to collect from Vlad. He's going to be happy.
You screwed that pooch good, asshole.
I told you! We should've switched cars!
The key to his heart was in the cars. Now go put a bullet through it.
Not pretty job but necessary to show strength. We destroy Mr Stone's mall like Soviet Russia tanks on war road. You take all money you can find and leave nothing standing up.
Who let them in? What the fuck!?
Sewers. Why did it have to be sewers.
Get that body over to the scanner.
The gold is inside the safe. Drill it open!
Bile is going to need some help to find you. Light a flare!
The manager will likely be around the back. His type don't spend much time with the plebs. Black suit, balding.
Guys, I can't read you. If you're still in there, GET OUT!
One more !
You're not gonna like it when I get angry, eh!
The drill stopped!
Get a flare going so Bile can find you!
What are you doing?
Keep the civilians down!
This should keep the guards busy.
How's Vlad? That adrenaline is not going to keep him stable for much longer, but Jiu Feng should be there soon, so just hang on.
We were in this enemy compound in Cambodia and my handler got eaten by a tiger. Dwankie kak he was. My handler, not the tiger.
Hook the winches up to the floor!
We can use that PA system to draw the scientists out of the laboratory.
We don't want to take too long. We've got a boss to hit.
... Drop 'em!
You guys see what happened to Pink?
Forget Locke for now, we'll take care of that scumbag later.
Blerrie! Looks like the Feds are here too. Commissioner Garrett must be really, really pissed, yeah?
He's locked himself in his vault, the crazy Ivan! Break it open. I'm sending you a thermal drill.
There's definitely more caches around here... We could leave 'em... Or... Not.
I can't shake 'em!
Turn those valves off.
C4 is waiting for you. What are you waiting for?
We have information about the Mendoza cashflow. Over $100 million from their American operations. We want to send a message - their money and their weapons are null and void.
Too slow, try again.
Looks like the curator's basement office.
We can settle for this...
We'll make some nice money off these weapons. Grab them, and let's go.
Looks like a Christmas tree to me! Go shake it! See what happens!
Pick up the pace, or we can kiss those plates goodbye!
Where's the blerrie alarm getting its power?
Just attach the cable to the pick-up and the hatch.
That's a keycard alright. Take it!
Halfway now, just two more overrides to go.
And the code is....1138!
That's the tablet PC. Perfect.
Have you found all the missing pieces yet? Check the shrine for clues.
You should be looking for recipes friends!
You look like rats in a maze. No cheese at the end for you though. Only assfuck.
Keep at it.
There's a bunch of rooms in the maintenance tunnels. Check all of them.
Shit, there's another guard here
That worked like a charm. Well fought and well carried out if you know what I mean. Payday is coming our way, well deserved.
The bartender was supposed to leave a maintenance box open somewhere. Find it.
Take the cooler with you!
Great. Now, please, keep the cops away from the time lock.
Get that thermite back to the vault.
Gotta take that laser system offline.
I've left you a keycard, an arc cutter and some breaching charges, my friends. I could press a button and open a door, but we must hide my involvement, yes.
Hit the boarding ramp controls.
Bag it up!
Thought you guys were stable? What the fuck happened back there?
Your first job is getting into the depot. Scout the area, check for cameras and guards. Keep it quiet.
Great. Here comes the guest list now.
Go for it, you chops.
I think... Just maybe... You'll do it.
He's approaching the trunk and...
Gentlemen? Please?
Guys, defend me! Those snipers are making it impossible for me to get close enough. You need to take them out!
Help! HELP!
Alright, time for me to dash!
18 more needed!
Power has been cut to the office! You gotta restore it!
Eye in the sky - watch out!
That's the house. Go on in, he's probably taking the air.
I'm almost there, get ready!
A bit hairy in the end but you got there. I don't think we could have gotten another penny from those chops. Nice work!
See what useful items you can find!
You lost? It looks like the admin office is on the lower deck.
Hell if I know. I think somebody hired Esteban to mess with me, but that's just answering a question with another damn question.
I reckon he's going to worry about his body too in little while, yeah?
I heard something...
Alright we got enough now, let's go!

There'll be a couple of keycards out there, maybe in the trunks of cars. They'll help you get silent access to the vault. Or you can forget that Mission Impossible crap and unleash Ragnarok. Up to you.
Is that one of GenSec's armored cash transports? If you open it we could get some additional cash from this job.
It's on the other side of the building.
Probably worth a fortune.
Hand me the reactor, quickly now!
Gunship's firing! Move! Move!
A goat got into an apartment up there. Get after it! Look for a way in.
Three charges on the wall should be enough.
Okay, guys. Bile dropped the EMP just outside the lumber mill. Go get it!
We want the Mendoza cash stream stopped completely. Their entire cash reserve is here in DC. To get to it we need to disarm their soldiers by destroying their weapons cache.
... Getting closer!
Good job. Four bags is good enough to go and do the trade.
You see it? Water fuckin' running down the wall. Totally fucked!
I don't believe in fate, for if I did, none of what I achieved ever would have come to me.
Could be a while. Was it left at the Union or....?
Good job. You sealed off one of the entrances. That should make it easier to defend.
We gotta get outta here!
This is bullshit, man.
Good call, now we have to see about getting you past the security gate to the vault.
That's what we heard, yeah.
Before we can do anything else, I need access to the rig's central network. Find the server room.
As I understand it, you had a little jol with my old proteg and some domkops a while back. I taught her all she knows about hacking, you know?
Such a waste, all this space, for that Mexican shit and his Coyopas...
You've got to fix the turntable!
Stop the cops!
Find me the list, gang. Just plug it into an online terminal in IT.
OK, time to steal some cars.
Those crates should work as a hiding place. Drop both bodies there. Get a body bag for the other guy.
This is an FBI auxiliary office... The hornet's nest. For the love of god stay quiet.
We're outta here.
Look what a nice guy I am. I had one of my contacts stash more body bags for you.
Look at this! The shutters on the case malfunctioned! That electrical mess in the lab must've screwed up the whole campus. Happy accidents!
BFD needs cooling. Refill the tank with water. Hurry!
There's no such thing as a master code.
Open sesame, yeah? Now get going further in. It's only going to get worse from here.
You've got to light a flare for Bile to land.
This is Bile, your pilot...
Let's bag up those weapons, yeah?
The pump's fixed! Protect the generator while we finish up here.
There's the alarm, gentlemen. Start the countdown.
Haha, you guys give new meaning to going loud.

Locke has us hitting a Murky facility out in the desert. Black Ridge. Was an old air force place, back in the day. Murkywater bought it up after the Cold War, turned it into their own Fort Knox, so you can bet they're holding some serious loot here. Not sure what to expect. Not much online, so we got little in the way of intel. One thing is certain though - you're not going to sneak through this one. Dress for loud.
The code you have has been disabled, but I think the system has a master code. Let me do some digging.

You've really put the shits up Murkywater, man. They're moving a large portion of their cash reserves away from the East Coast. Heavily guarded cargo plane, yeah. For sure. It's gonna be most vulnerable when its in flight so I'm smuggling you onto that plane. Deal with the guards, open the cargo doors and let that money spill down. Hardly sounds like work at all, huh?
Locked. Damn it! Alright, stay cool. Find the manager. Take him hostage. I'm sure he can help us get in.
Ok, here comes the second wave!
I hear ya.....shit.
They've really opened the valve. The van can't wait forever. You need to book it, now!
Great job, guys! That server is worth a lot of cash right now. Don't drop it.
Those railcars are locked down. That card should help with that.
Okay, looks like they have two linked locks on this. Find the other lock and get a breaker on it too.
Prep the next part, and hope nothing bad happens.
This is it. Commissar's apartment. Get through.
Got it! That was some outstanding flying, if I say so myself.
Maybe our new Medic Dozers will make you reconsider...
Safe house vault is going to be a little crowded tonight. Nicely done, folks.
Good job, taking out that alarm.
They put the fire out with their feet!
The laptop's inside that house. Do whatever it takes to get it.
Get access to the control room.
That's it? The briefcase? Perfect! Now we can get outta here!
What the hell is going on up there, shitwipe?!
The skid loader won't get past that container unless you get it out of the way.
The van won't be able to stay long. You gotta move fast when it arrives!
Excellent. We're almost done. Bear with me.
I've got an idea about what we can use those for later!
That's the coke, gang. I knew you would do it! Now bag it.
Been to the wine cellar yet?
No time to brew coffee for that pissed old fart. Keep him safe. I'm sending an extraction now.
OK, I can't stay here forever!
Don't mind that one, I'll get that one!
Looks like there might be an underground vault somewhere.
Nice. That's it. Alright, one of you guys monkey up there.
Don't just stand around, get in there.
Hold on...
Can't get out of there on an empty tank. Fuel the plane!
Pick up the phone and put me through.
Good. Now find the second keycard.
Could be a while. Was it Maryland or Massachussetts Ave?
And off we go my friends!
All right. Try and keep out of sight. It's all about control.
I'll be there in one minute.
Hold on until he's in the tree!
We want to cause a blowout in the main drill, but the rig has a safeguard against that very thing. You can disable it from the control room.
If you can get inside the main building there's a server room on the first floor where you can hack into the camera feed and help locate Vlad.
Aim the weapon, friends.
Where's the shit?
Check that place for the competition.
That's some fine loot they stashed in there, but it's ours now. How do we get it out?
They cut the power! Get it back up!
Shit!
Don't let anything happen to the skid loader.
Great! We're in!
You gotta get the security bars open. Crack open the card reader near it.
There it is! Get through the gate and secure both the BCI headset and the software.
You have to destroy that evidence!
Time to get our Ukrainian out of that container!
We need more.
Now see how you can get access to the vault.
Over there!
Another blocker. It's locked down. Get to the main computer in the server room an hack it, yeah?
You need to set up the drill.
Bile is in-bound. Be ready for him!
There soon.
Nice, bring the money to the van.
Sorry, that wasn't right.
Stay on your toes. This's gonna be tense.
You're going to need to do the cook yourself.
Now subdue the auctioneer so you can get his keycard.
You are one stupid asshole!
Gonna miss giving that arsehole Roscoe a sound thrashing. Maybe we could break him out too?
The saw stopped running.
Hang on, sipping trash?
You guys know who Tucker is? I hope you don't. Great work back there.
Fuel tank is full, well done.
Answer the phone!
You can't stay there!
Ah! Gentlemen! Greetings!
Fok voort, add some!
Luck favors the prepared.
Now find the storage room. That's where the keys'll be.
Use the zipline up to the bridge! The train is the only way out!
That's all of 'em! Nice!
Looks like they've upped the security. Gotta find a way to get the shutters open without making a mess of the Oval Office.
Scope out the manager's office. You should be able to find who the IT guy is. Then you can hack his pc.
Naaah, He'll be fine.
...and cross your fingers.
My friends, Vlad needs some small help with wedding planning.
I'm like God damn Mother Teresa here!
Here! Here!
We got what we came for. Activate the engine!
If you can keep this from going loud you're probably a lot better off.
Maybe some Minigun Dozers will shut you up...
Get the cocaine from the van!
Ach! They've cut the power at the emergency shutdown point. Find the lever and pull it back to continue charging.
Cameras? And guards? Vlad didn't say anything about this!
Damn, are those drones? We're really living in the future, aren't we? They seem to have a camera so stay out of sight.
He bought it. The time has come to kill Mr. Sosa. Give him my regards.
Can't you find the code?
The Sosa Cartel has attacked one of my shipments in the Caribbean. They must pay, and you will collect this payment.
Keep the cops away so it doesn't stop cutting.
Locke got away, but we'll have our payback later.
The power is down. You need to restore it.
Hell, Commissar just sent more coke straight down the pan. Hurry before it's all gone!
Before we can do anything else, I need access to the rig's central network. One of the lab workers should have the server room keycard.
Move that barrel. Quickly now.
Drive into the door with the forklift!
The Federales are pumping gas through the ventilation system! Stay away from it until it dissipates!
That's the helicopter. Get on it, crew!
You get into that computer yet?
They bought it. Keep working.
Get the power back up friends.
You may rely on me as always.
I knew I could count on you, my friends!
If you chops find a guitar case full of guns... just let it be, yeah?
You gotta get that code.
The trains are leaving! Set the explosives, quick!
It's the clowns! It's the fucking clowns from the news!
...Plan is as follows.
Elevator's here! Fasten the steel wire between the security door and the elevator through the hatch. Then shoot the cable. Oh, and stand back.
Sweet Mother Mary, please let me live another day... I'm a good boy, aren't I?
Do NOT let them see the hacking device when we get it up and running!
I see nine of them.
See anything with historical significance?
I've never SEEN so much money go to waste! Get the last of it, come on!
Good day, my friends.
If you don't want to carry any more, set off an ink bomb on the rest to ruin it for the triad. It's a nice way to show them how we feel, too.
Fuck!
Oooh, stealing some shit, are we? I like it. Anything to make these fucking bikers' lives miserable. Put it in the trunk and I'll take it with me as I drive off. We'll deal with the details later!
Chopper's nearly there. Just hold on!
If you take the cable and hook it up to the vault, we can pull it out.
My friends - you help me with small problem, yes? I need you to cause... Domestic problem.
You need to get inside that warehouse. No telling what state Vlad is in!
Alright, I'm in, hold on...
Look out the window - Taxman is the guy in the white shirt.
We're looking good. Looking good.
Those motel rooms look like good candidates for a little wrecking. Get in there and get your rockstar on. Smash the TV's, lamps - anything you can find.
Well, you got a decent amount. Just about covers the gas money. Maybe next time we can push it further.
Find the nearby power box and disable it. Should kill those metal detectors.
I want you to go in, you get them back from the (fucking police) before they leave warehouse. You are now in great hurry, if you understand.
I can't dust 'em off!
You need to get some explosives onto the gate.
Time to get aboard and leave!
Blerrie, there's a domkop in the office. You gotta get him out of there.
The deposit boxes are a bit of a lottery, but I know there is a lot of cash here. Find it, and bag it.
What's this? A gun? Oh, yeah!
So long you fucker!
Have you found the barman?
What? That must've been the wrong tile!
That's the first. Ah, such a small thing, but enough to wipe out Washington.
The blimp could be all the way across Nevada and would see those.
Stand by, gang. Organizing an exit. Hold the line!
You're really gonna try and hijack a train to get past the Army's roadblocks? Guess I'll believe it when I see it.
Every second counts, gang! Get to that coke while there's still some left!
Where's the shit?
Make your way to the vault in the casino.
Thankfully, I have a supply of C4 right here.
That's the guard dealt with. No need to worry about the cameras now.
I can't fucking shake 'em!
Man, you guys are a train wreck. What a fuckin' mess.
Did I ever tell you about the time Hajrudin tried to steal a slot machine from a casino in Vegas? Fuck, it wasn't pretty.
Keep it going in there.
Something's gone wrong with the turntable! Looks like a circuit shorted out. Fix it as fast as you can.
Of course we have a very diverse workforce. In fact, I just got out of a conference with our Latin division. Empty the bin
That floor needs to be blown open, yeah?
Now get to the vault and assemble that rig.
This server has secrets, recordings, data that can change the world. And all my saved games. Yeah, for sure.
Ok, go, go go! Get out of there!
There it is. But step carefully! Those floor tiles are pressure sensitive. Don't step on them! You'll have to make a safe path across! Use the circuit box over there.
Looks like every helicopter in the Washington PD is on our ass!
Here I am!
Escape is here, whenever you're ready.
You gotta find some clues. Keep looking.
Get that server to the van! You got it!
The intel's behind a voice recognition lock. Our man on the inside hid some bugging devices near you. Use them to get a few recordings of Esteban.
Blerrie, the charging has stopped. Start it up again, yeah?
Find some, and pour it in, yeah?
You need to charge the gun again to fire.
Come on, gang. You've gotta get the crane in position.
Hurry now, get to the canteen!
You've got to keep at least 6 bags!
You'll need something special for that door. Go check the armory!
Fish in this town grow fat on corpses.
The hacking was stopped! Go restart it!
OK, I'm inside. I'll get to work on these servers. Keep me covered!
That's it. Dock gate's opened. Now let's get the ship moving. We have the comm frequency. Just find the radio and patch me in.
Don't' forget the door, yeah?
Bile is waiting for you!
Sail out of the blast zone!
Activate the power box to turn on the signal light.
YES FRIENDS! Oh, sorry... I'm not used to this sneaking about, yeah?
Whatever you're doing, keep doing it.
Get Vlad's jewelry to the garbage truck!
Look for Twitch in the alley!
There we go. That will come in handy. Now, there's a lever that controls those bollards. Get them lowered and keep going, yeah?
Perfect!
Sure, alright. There you go.
You know, I think I just realized the gravity of what we're doing.
You wanted me here, here I am. Let's get this over with.
Hydrogen... Is that a gas... Can't be a solid... Says add it. You guys got a gas tank?
Ten seconds now!
We're wasting time. Find what you need to get inside the office.
We're after the rat. He's probably in the bus. You know what to do.
Now, pop some smoke out there so the pilot knows where to drop the equipment.
The broken window gave you away!
Gonna give you a faceful of lead!
Good start, now get the rest!
OK, enough money making, take the recording and make a run for it, unless you wanna hang around for more loot.
I can't believe this shit!
That's the front and the upstairs dark as far as cameras are concerned. Cameras in the vault area run on a seperate circuit though.
Watch out, sniper's set up inside that building nearby.
.. or stay, if you're feeling greedy.
Achh! That vehicle has got to be removed!
Wait, you didn't get ALL of the goats. Is my asshole your plaything? I want ALL the goats.
Guys! I'm waiting for bags!
Leavin' in ten!
One more minute, then I got to scram!
If you guys wanna keep going, Vlad's giving us a bonus for everything over 50k!
Truck's moving. Stay with it!
That's a strange looking dinges, yeah? Put in on a zipline, chop chop!
We're not leaving without lining our pockets. Use the keycard and go for the gold.
You find a way into that office yet? We need to get our hands on the laptop.
There's the beautiful cash. Get bagging it, crew!
Okay, time for...honesty. The coke is packed in...goats. Yes, goats. And they've escaped. Haha, tricky goats, huh?! Find them!
Nicely done, friends. That's what we're looking for.
Get that C4 on the door.
This is where you're going to be dropped off.
See if you can find some batteries to power it, then set them up, yeah?
Seems like the deal was a gold arms transaction. Made here in DC.
That's The Dentist's loot saved. Bail now, or really show The Grin how we treat Vegas DC-style.
He put it inside his shirt.
Look in all the sanctum rooms if you haven't found everything you need.
Cops screwed the hack. Reboot it!
I'm sending the boat, keep bagging the stuff!
Armory access granted.
That's enough...
Just raise the balloon when you're done, groovers!
That's one taken care of. Time to do the next.
What are you waiting for? Take care of the vault.
Great job keeping it quiet. They don't suspect you, so the containers are unlocked. Have at it!
*whistles* There it is. What a beauty.
The vault with the artifact is behind these doors. You gotta get them open, friends.
You've got to bring him the right car key!
What the hell are you doing here?
Get at the vault, you'll need to get past security.
Hurry now, you gotta follow Bain!
Keep it under control.
Moretta is moored at Dock 2B. Can't access it there.
Stop walking around and go inside the room.
Alright, I'm back in.
Abashed the devil stood and felt how awful goodness is
column3: and saw Virtue in her shape how lovely: and pined his loss.""

String: Blerrie! This whole operation just went to kak!
Use ziplines if you want to speed it up.
They knew we were comin'. Gimme a second here...
Copy that. Let me pull it up...it's 8394. Don't let it get out.
Who is this? Who the fuck are you!?
This whole enterprise will be for nothing if you don't get that time lock tick-tocking again.
Get in there. Meet up with Mitchell.
Why are we here? What's going on?
Sweet, I'm getting this for myself.
...You'll need to find the box's shelf number by hacking a terminal in the computer lab.
Blerrie, they've outfitted the Cloakers with cuffs, now!
This one is tail I can't lose!
I'm gonna fucking kill you!
Almost through the vault door. Get ready.
Hey they might be workers but they're not dumb and blind - keep your profile low.
Let me get this straight. You got a guy named Dallas who ain't from Dallas, and a guy called Houston who's never been to Houston?
Something's not right here. Sound the alarm!
Get the loot out of there!
OK, we're into the railcar. Use the camera to see what's inside.
We shouldn't have spent so much money so quickly
BFD broke down. Gonna need tools to repair it.
Which way does this GPS go? Is Texas north or south? I think I'm on the right street.
Have a careful look around. Stay clear of Wang's guards.
We're going for a roof pick-up. Start shifting those bags to the top of the bank and put the cage together.
Okay, hit the middle and right console. Go!
Politics is as you know global - I need you for a global effort.
The pillar! Move! Move!
Second truck opened! Check it!
You should get in cover for a moment and make sure it's ok.
All agents will be eligible to receive one piece of pie, per friday, per rotation cycle. Coffee will still be available freely, but as the frenchman said, you'll have to get yer own darn tea.
Well, in the annals of criminal cock-ups, that ranks high. I can hear the cops laughing from here. Better luck next time.
Good evening, sir.
Your limbs must be screaming now. But not as much as if you stop grabbing those safes.
One of you guys pick up the phone!
Mr Blonde is waiting on us to get the cops off him!
Nothing happened? Must be the wrong one. Keep looking.
The emp will give us a way in but it's primary function is to take care of the test subjects for us. If the stories are true, we don't want to take these guys on.
Your adventure is over, you goat-fuck.
30 seconds to pickup, guys!
Keep an eye on all entry points, especially the ladders.
Guys. Operate the crane. Get it into position.
You gotta go back and check the mainframe again for the second artifact. Make it fast, yeah?
Now, let's make some real money. Figure out how to access the barns. That should be where they keep the weapons workshop.
The office door has a keypad. Let's hope the code's written down somewhere.
What are you looking at?
Oh, you know we aren't leaving without some of those weapons. We just need to get them out of here some way...
I'm back in. *whispers* There is no spoon.
...They're on us! They're on us... hang tight till I can get a backup ride...
What's in these boxes?
Make sure you look around everywhere.
We had a scheduling conflict. Major account holder turned up a day early. Big account from... Uh... Kiribati.
Up top!
A nice quiet entrance, yeah? They never heard you coming. So get to it.
Come on, get past the gate! There's no time to lose!
Dammit! SWAT ambush. I didn't see it!
No good working with all that gas, find a way to turn it off!
Saw through that roof and drag him out!
Dwankie chop! I would like to kick his teeth in.
Unless you still want the cops to show up you better be careful around those workers
That's one bag!
We gotta get outta here!
You're so close to Stage 6! So! Freaking! Close!
Yo, There's one!
Why does that not fill my head with confidence? If you're going to stay, then sit back and be quiet.
The Murkywater trains will be locked by some kind of security panel. We'll most likely have to hack them to get the doors open.
Okay friends, time to crack this nut. Find a way in.

Well done, friends. We got what we came for, but that last... we need to figure out our next move. After you left the warehouse, Murkywater comms went completely dark, off the grid. First World Bank. Hello, can I help you? Hello? Are you having trouble breathing? Mr Sheen, do we have to talk about this again!?

Hurry now, get a drill on that door.
What are you waiting for? Cut the door open!
Get bagging the money, gang!
Use any method you can to pass through that front gate. There's more than one way to skin a cat...Yeesh, that's a dark saying, isn't it?
What are you waiting for, fire the cannon!
Ach! Can't get to him quietly. Let's see what he's up to. Plant a listening device.
Good work, now get into the sanctum!
Open up!
Everything is under control. We'll have a good haul on this trip.
You tricked him. Excellent. Now kill him.
Alright, I'm in. I'll pop that lock for you in a sec. Right now I need you to get back out front, grab the C4 and get it on the street.

Get to that pillar - move!

Okay, the last elf fell off the shelf, yes. Fuck him. Time to leave and enjoy your Christmas bonus, friends!
Take that ladder, my friends. Take it, and profit!
In dentistry, I have become very appreciative of people who keep things... clean.
That's the first bag. That's what we need, but keep going.
That damn barrier is preventing the drill from coming down. Get to security and open it.
The Glitter Room might be worth checking for a laptop.
Marked a computer. Log me in and I'll deal with this.
BFD's guzzled a whole coolant tank already. Fill her glass, gang. Bathroom's have water.
Bain is heading for the roof, try to keep up with him, yeah?

How's it look in there?

Tell me if you are feeling sick. Or if hair fall out. Or balls fall off.

Time to start looking for that stash of Murky loot. We're looking for cash, and lots of it.
Yo, we're outta here.

Hello friends.

Move to the parking lot for extraction.

You're the buffest bag boy around!

There you go, now do the last one.

Grab your oh-shit handles!

Hang tight till I come back for another round!

Now bring the encryption keys back to Hoxton so he can get to work on the next server.

That fucking book.

The facility is located on an island in international waters off the coast of northern Oregon and has been in used by the Murkies since the 70s. I have pulled in a couple favors and bought you a ticket on a small civvy submarine so that you can sneak into the place and get our man back.

Ok friends, get ready!

Listen up! Someone has tipped off the cops about suspicious activity at the Safe House. Units are on their way as we speak to do a search and seizure. They don't know it's you, though - boy are they in for a surprise.

Okay, Dallas. It's been two years since we worked together, and I need to see that you still got what it takes. We'll start with something simple, all right? An acquaintance of mine recently got robbed on a cocaine deal by some low-life mobster. I need to you to break into his night club and see if you can find the stolen cocaine and get it back. Easy, right?

You need to complete the formula, prepare the next ingredient.

Look for a way to get Esteban's prints off a hard surface. Some tape would work nice.
Barbarians are what you are! Barbarians!
Looks like the key tag needs a higher level coding for the armory. You'll have to recode it.
Get out there and fix that turntable!
What an idiot. It's Mandarin.... and you don't want to know.
Don't be gentle. Just throw that shit in.
